  "body": "### Describe the feature\n\nI am using `hardhat_metadata` to determine what was the actual state from which the node was forked at/from and use that to reset the node at the end of some action using `hardhat_reset`. `hardhat_reset` requires you to pass the `jsonRpcUrl` from which to get the fork data. However, since `hardhat_metadata` does not expose current forkUrl you are required to hardcode it.\n\n### Search terms\n\nhardhat_metadata",
